config:
  theme: dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client / SDK
    participant Frontend as Dynamo Frontend + KV Router<br/>(Gateway / API / Routing / KV Index State)
    participant PrefillSidecar as Prefill Dynamo Sidecar
    participant PrefillEngine as Native Prefill Engine Server<br/>(vLLM)
    participant DecodeSidecar as Decode Dynamo Sidecar
    participant DecodeEngine as Native Decode Engine Server<br/>(vLLM)

    Client->>Frontend: Send request<br/>(prompt, params, stream=true)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Authenticate / authorize
    Frontend->>Frontend: Normalize to Dynamo request schema
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select prefill worker using KV router

    Frontend->>PrefillSidecar: Forward Dynamo prefill request

    PrefillSidecar->>PrefillSidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine prefill request schema
    PrefillSidecar->>PrefillEngine: Invoke prefill over OpenEngine API

    PrefillEngine->>PrefillEngine: Normalize to vLLM prefill request schema
    PrefillEngine->>PrefillEngine: Execute prefill<br/>(prompt processing + KV cache population)

    PrefillEngine-->>PrefillSidecar: Return prefill result over OpenEngine API<br/>(KV transfer params, usage, errors)
    PrefillSidecar->>PrefillSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo prefill response schema

    PrefillSidecar-->>Frontend: Return Dynamo prefill response<br/>(KV transfer params)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Update KV router state from prefill result
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select decode worker using KV router

    Frontend->>DecodeSidecar: Forward Dynamo decode request<br/>(KV transfer params, params)

    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeSidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine decode request schema
    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeEngine: Invoke decode over OpenEngine API

    DecodeEngine->>DecodeEngine: Normalize to vLLM decode request schema
    DecodeEngine->>DecodeEngine: Attach KV transfer params
    DecodeEngine->>DecodeEngine: Execute decode<br/>(generate tokens from transferred KV)

    DecodeEngine-->>DecodeSidecar: Stream response over OpenEngine API<br/>(tokens, usage, finish reason, errors)
    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo response schema

    DecodeSidecar-->>Frontend: Stream Dynamo response
    Frontend-->>Client: Stream response

    par Event plane
        PrefillEngine-->>PrefillSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / KV events / metrics)
        PrefillSidecar->>PrefillSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        PrefillSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(capacity / KV metadata / request status)

        DecodeEngine-->>DecodeSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / KV events / metrics)
        DecodeSidecar->>DecodeSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        DecodeSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(capacity / KV metadata / request status)
    and State update
        Frontend->>Frontend: Update KV router state<br/>(KV index, worker capacity, request status)
    end
